{"tid":1214231,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"好仔唔當差既年代又返黎","createTime":"2019-06-13T03:49:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T04:34:51.000Z","uid":202804,"like":30,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"3bd7d69b31bdc3b9ddd1c1b660eda10b5b965b76","tid":1214231,"uid":202804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T03:49:58.000Z","msg":"經過左琴日<br />\n以後你老豆老母仲好意思叫你考公務員去考警察既話<br />\n唔該你地屌醒班廢老<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢個年頭, 做警察唔係一件風光既事<br />\n小學幼稚園老師要重新思考下係咪要教育下一代<br />\n「警察叔叔係幫我地捉壞人 ,儆惡懲奸」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我淨係見到10幾個速龍小隊圍9後生仔<br />\n棍棍都出盡全力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n將人飛起撻生魚咁撻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n開槍下下都瞄頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b88bc603c07d9da8c2c31636adbded7cab115d5","tid":1214231,"uid":202804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T03:53:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37ae1280da4e4a473e4fee6335ba62645b3bbddd","tid":1214231,"uid":202804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T03:57:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b531ca1abc9abf9cfb2301a307a9649539fe0cf","tid":1214231,"uid":204790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T03:58:09.000Z","msg":"我都有諗過，其實係唔係因為老一輩開始傳呢個觀念落黎，所以所有好仔都唔當差，全部垃圾去哂當差，搞到今時今日警察啲質素變到咁樣"},{"pid":"1b7ee7cc9715b065b105a022b5d139defaa8eff7","tid":1214231,"uid":202804,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid